narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes! For sure! The workload is manageable and the course is beyond interesting!
Take this course if you are interested in art history, American history, or analysis. Hopefully it will be renewed because it is crucial to an understanding of modern art.
Excellent course that offers a fresh new perspective on Art History and the role of the black artist within it.
